CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 27, 2005

[Cite as 04/27/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1880.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2005-0231. State ex rel. Badock v. McMonagle.

In Mandamus. On respondents’ answer and motion for summary judgment. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed.

Mover, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
